{"tid":1510414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有去遊行的200萬和理非，全部十點鐘大嗌","createTime":"2019-08-27T07:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T09:40:53.000Z","uid":761,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"06dfa22a3b5e2907b804fd3d7d657898e8d5087c","tid":1510414,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"相信聲音可大到轟天動地，何其壯觀！<br />\n<br />\n香港有200萬人反對政府，但街頭抗爭門檻太高，普通市民根本無法落場，應該要有一些簡單活動畀多些人可以參與，維持聲勢，十點大嗌係好主意，但要向親友宣傳下，好多人都未知咩事<br />\n嗌撚到班藍絲驚<br />\n落街都唔好咁大聲講野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q9dMAp2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9dMAp2.jpg&h=1fed8120&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HoTHTbJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHoTHTbJ.jpg&h=271c9a98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h8MBXDp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh8MBXDp.png&h=6fd8008c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9GnahDq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9GnahDq.jpg&h=e14de9b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"442cc6ddec69e2034a18483ca32b3d7e900ab55c","tid":1510414,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:26:33.000Z","msg":"呀"},{"pid":"a0e8bf6e3c432d4d67b6c781c093fdf800690f12","tid":1510414,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:26:51.000Z","msg":"呀"},{"pid":"f79616f54cba8fda72b3b748ea130ca1e9532517","tid":1510414,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi%2FGl%2B26p